Coretti Arle Titz https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coretti_Arle_Titz 0 Coretti Genrichovna Arle-Titz (December 5, 1883 – December 15, 1951), also known as Corette Alefred, was an American-born jazz, spiritual, and pop music singer (lyrical and dramatic soprano), dancer and actress who was well known in the Russian Empire and the Soviet Union.
